---
---
<section class="why-learn" id="why-learn">
  <div class="why-learn-inner">
    <div class="why-header">
      <h2 class="display-headline why-headline reveal">
        If I've got my sums right,<br />you're here for one of<br /><em>3 reasons.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="why-reasons">
      <div class="why-reason why-reason--1 reveal">
        <p class="body-lora why-reason-text">
          You're after something legit. Something <strong>halal</strong>. Something you can start as a beginner and grow into a full-time income.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-reason why-reason--2 reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.12s">
        <p class="body-lora why-reason-text">
          You're done swapping your time for a salary when you should be <strong>spending your time with your loved ones</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-reason why-reason--3 reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.24s">
        <p class="body-lora why-reason-text">
          You want to build something that gives you the <strong>freedom to live life on your own terms</strong> and leaves something real behind for the people you love.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="body-lora why-intro reveal">
      Did I catch that right? Well so did everyone who graduated from our Kickstarter Academy.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-learn {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 130px 0 100px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .why-learn-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why-header {
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .why-headline {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4.5vw, 64px);
    color: var(--color-near-black);
  }

  .why-headline em {
    color: var(--color-amazon);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── Circles row ── */
  .why-reasons {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .why-reason {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 56px;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .why-reason:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  .why-reason--1 { background: #e07c12; }
  .why-reason--2 { background: #c45e05; }
  .why-reason--3 { background: #8f3c02; }

  .why-reason-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
  }

  .why-reason-text strong {
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .why-intro {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #555;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 56px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .why-learn { padding: 72px 0 64px; }
    .why-learn-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    .why-header { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .why-reasons { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 24px; }
  }
</style>
